          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-blue-200 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-blue-100 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-6xl font-light text-gray-100 group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">03</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Build</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We build the system, integrate it into your existing tools, and set up operational guardrails.</p>
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 -right-3 transform -translate-y-1/2 z-10">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-blue-200 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-blue-100 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-6xl font-light text-gray-100 group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">04</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Operate</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We operate the system with you or for you, handling execution while you maintain strategic control.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY THIS MODEL SECTION -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block mb-4">
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Why This Model</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Leverage Without Adding Headcount
