        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          You set direction and priorities. We execute inside the system with full visibility. Your business scales without adding operational overhead.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Left Column -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">You Stay in Control</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Set strategic direction and priorities</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
